         There is one part of the PnP I will happily violate since it infringes on the right of free speech:</P><P>"you will not communicate the existence of any such exploitable bug (bugs that grant the user unnatural or unintended benefits in game), either directly or through public posting, to any other user of EverQuest"</P><P>That means that we, as human beings, are not allowed to discuss exploitable bugs on this message board.  This is offensive to me on many levels.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
